%e A002504 From _Rémi Guillaume_, Dec 07 2023: (Start)
%e A002504 1 + 3*7*6 = 127 = A002407(5) is the 5th prime of this form, so a(5) = 7.
%e A002504 1 + 3*10*9 = 271 = A002407(6) is the 6th prime of this form, so a(6) = 10.
%e A002504 (End)
